Package: myfirstpkg
Title: Example R Package
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Emily", "Potts", , "epotts5@jh.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides simple functions for basic arithmetic operations, including add_numbers for adding two numeric values and subtract_numbers for calculating the difference between two numbers. It is designed as an easy-to-use tool for practicing package creation and function implementation in R.
